OL,6,FIt came out after the final part of a
OL,7,Fspecial Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,8,Freview into the care of Calocane by
OL,9,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,10,FFoundation Trust (NHFT) found risk
OL,11,Fassessments "minimised or omitted" key
OL,12,Fdetails of the serious risk he posed
OL,13,Fto others.
OL,15,FIn response to the CQC findings,
OL,16,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS Trust
OL,17,Fsaid it's "truly sorry" that
OL,18,F"sometimes we have let down patients
OL,19,Fand families", and that it has made
OL,20,Fimprovements to staff and safety.
