OL,6,FSpeaking after the announcement Emma
OL,7,FWebber said:
OL,9,F"We welcome the confirmation from the
OL,10,FPrime Minister that the public inquiry
OL,11,Fwill be, as asked for by all three
OL,12,Ffamilies, a statutory judge led one.
OL,14,F"Given the level of catastrophic
OL,15,Ffailures wrought upon us by the NHS
OL,16,FMental Health Trust, Nottinghamshire
OL,17,FPolice and Leicestershire Police, this
OL,18,Fis the only possible consideration.
